question: Who has received the immunization Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free?

question: Which payer paid for the medication Digoxin 0.125 MG Oral Tablet?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX pl: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral> SELECT DISTINCT ?description WHERE { ?medication a syn:Medication; syn:description 'Digoxin 0.125 MG Oral Tablet'^^pl:; syn:payerId ?payerId. ?payer a syn:Payer; syn:id ?payerId; syn:name ?name.}
sql: SELECT DISTINCT py.name FROM medications med LEFT JOIN payers py ON med.payer=py.id WHERE med.description='Digoxin 0.125 MG Oral Tablet';
cypher: MATCH (py:Payer)-[:HAS_COVERED]->(m:Medication {description: 'Digoxin 0.125 MG Oral Tablet'}) RETURN DISTINCT py.name;
mql: db.patients.aggregate([    { $match: { "ENCOUNTERS.MEDICATIONS.DESCRIPTION": "Digoxin 0.125 MG Oral Tablet" } },    { $lookup: {            from: "payers",            localField: "ENCOUNTERS.PAYER_REF",            foreignField: "PAYER_ID",            as: "patient_payers"        }},    { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS" },    { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS.MEDICATIONS" },    { $unwind: "$patient_payers"},    { $match: { "ENCOUNTERS.MEDICATIONS.DESCRIPTION": "Digoxin 0.125 MG Oral Tablet" } },    { $group: {        _id: "$patient_payers.NAME"    }},    { $project: { _id: 0, payer: "$_id" } }])

question: Give me the encounters that are related to the immunization Hep B  adult.

question: Please provide me the payer that paid for the medication Alendronic acid 10 MG Oral Tablet.
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX pl: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral> SELECT DISTINCT ?description WHERE { ?medication a syn:Medication; syn:description 'Alendronic acid 10 MG Oral Tablet'^^pl:; syn:payerId ?payerId. ?payer a syn:Payer; syn:id ?payerId; syn:name ?name.}

mql: db.patients.aggregate([    { $match: { "ENCOUNTERS.MEDICATIONS.DESCRIPTION": "Alendronic acid 10 MG Oral Tablet" } },    { $lookup: {            from: "payers",            localField: "ENCOUNTERS.PAYER_REF",            foreignField: "PAYER_ID",            as: "patient_payers"        }},    { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS" },    { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS.MEDICATIONS" },    { $unwind: "$patient_payers"},    { $match: { "ENCOUNTERS.MEDICATIONS.DESCRIPTION": "Alendronic acid 10 MG Oral Tablet" } },    { $group: {        _id: "$patient_payers.NAME"    }},    { $project: { _id: 0, payer: "$_id" } }])

question: Who is associated with the organization SERENITY HILL NURSING CENTER?

mql: db.organizations.aggregate([    { $match: { "NAME": "SERENITY HILL NURSING CENTER" } },    { $lookup: {        from: "patients",        localField: "ORGANIZATION_ID",        foreignField: "ENCOUNTERS.ORGANIZATION_REF",        as: "op"    }},    { $unwind: "$op" },    { $group: {_id: { first: "$op.FIRST", last: "$op.LAST" } } },    { $project: {_id: 0, FIRST: "$_id.first", LAST: "$_id.last" } }])

cypher: MATCH (e:Encounter)-[:IS_ORDERED_DURING]->(p:Procedure {description: 'Assessment of health and social care needs (procedure)'}) RETURN DISTINCT e.description;
mql: db.patients.aggregate(    [{        $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.PROCEDURES.DESCRIPTION": "Assessment of health and social care needs (procedure)"}    },    {        $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS"    },    {        $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS.PROCEDURES"    },    {        $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.PROCEDURES.DESCRIPTION": "Assessment of health and social care needs (procedure)"}    },    {        $group: {            _id: {encounter_desc: "$ENCOUNTERS.DESCRIPTION"}        }    },    {        $project: {            _id: 0,            ENCOUNTERS_DESCRIPTION: "$_id.encounter_desc"        }    },    ]    )

question: Please provide names of the patients that are linked with the organization LEOMINSTER COMUNITY HEALTH CENTER.
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX pl: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral> SELECT DISTINCT ?first ?last WHERE { ?organization a syn:Organization; syn:id ?organizationId; syn:name 'LEOMINSTER COMUNITY HEALTH CENTER'^^pl:. ?encounter a syn:Encounter; syn:organizationId ?organizationId; syn:patientId ?patientId. ?patient a syn:Patient; syn:id ?patientId; syn:first ?first; syn:last ?last. }
sql: SELECT DISTINCT p.first, p.last FROM organizations org LEFT JOIN encounters e ON org.id=e.organization LEFT JOIN patients p ON e.patient=p.id WHERE org.name='LEOMINSTER COMUNITY HEALTH CENTER';
cypher: MATCH (o:Organization {name: 'LEOMINSTER COMUNITY HEALTH CENTER'})-[:IS_PERFOMED_AT]->(e:Encounter)<-[:HAS_ENCOUNTER]-(p:Patient) RETURN DISTINCT p.firstName, p.lastName
mql: db.organizations.aggregate([    { $match: { "NAME": "LEOMINSTER COMUNITY HEALTH CENTER" } },    { $lookup: {        from: "patients",        localField: "ORGANIZATION_ID",        foreignField: "ENCOUNTERS.ORGANIZATION_REF",        as: "op"    }},    { $unwind: "$op" },    { $unwind: "$op.ENCOUNTERS"},    { $match: { "NAME": "LEOMINSTER COMUNITY HEALTH CENTER" } },    { $group: {_id: {first: "$op.FIRST", last: "$op.LAST"}} },    { $project: {_id: 0, first: "$_id.first", last: "$_id.last" } }])

cypher: MATCH (p:Patient)-[:IS_ORDERED_FOR]->(s:Supply {description: 'Blood glucose testing strips (physical object)'}) RETURN DISTINCT p.firstName, p.lastName;
mql: db.patients.aggregate([    {        $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.SUPPLIES.DESCRIPTION": 'Blood glucose testing strips (physical object)'}    },    {        $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS"    },    {        $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS.SUPPLIES"    },    {        $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.SUPPLIES.DESCRIPTION": 'Blood glucose testing strips (physical object)'}    },    {        $group: {            _id: {                FIRST: "$FIRST",                LAST: "$LAST"            }        }    },    {        $project: {            _id: 0,            first: "$_id.FIRST",            last: "$_id.LAST"        }    },])

question: How many immunizations are uncovered by the payer with the ID 8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX uuid: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#urn:uuid> SELECT  ?uncoveredImmunizations WHERE { ?payer a syn:Payer; syn:id '8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce'^^uuid:; syn:uncoveredImmunizations ?uncoveredImmunizations. }
sql: SELECT uncovered_immunizations FROM payers WHERE id='8fa6c185-e44e-3e34-8bd8-39be8694f4ce';

question: What encounter is associated with the supply with the code 419343004?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX snomed: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#snomed:SNOMED-CT> SELECT DISTINCT ?description WHERE { ?supply a syn:Supply; syn:code '419343004'^^snomed:; syn:encounterId ?encounterid. ?encounter a syn:Encounter; syn:id ?encounterid; syn:description ?description. }
sql: SELECT DISTINCT e.description FROM supplies s LEFT JOIN encounters e ON s.encounter=e.id WHERE s.code='419343004';

question: What is the description of the device with code 706180003?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX snomed: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#snomed:SNOMED-CT> SELECT DISTINCT ?description WHERE { ?device a syn:Device; syn:code '706180003'^^snomed:; syn:description ?description. }
sql: SELECT description FROM devices WHERE code='706180003';

question: Please provide me the patient associated with the claim transaction fdb84e8a-3e20-b3a8-0cf1-cea85c87cfd2.
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX uuid: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#urn:uuid> SELECT  DISTINCT ?first ?last WHERE { ?claimtransaction a syn:ClaimTransaction;syn:id 'fdb84e8a-3e20-b3a8-0cf1-cea85c87cfd2'^^uuid:; syn:patientId ?patientId. ?patient a syn:Patient; syn:id ?patientId; syn:first ?first; syn:last ?last.}
sql: SELECT DISTINCT p.first, p.last FROM claims_transactions clt LEFT JOIN patients p ON clt.patientid=p.id WHERE clt.id='fdb84e8a-3e20-b3a8-0cf1-cea85c87cfd2';
mql: db.patients.aggregate([    {        $match: {            "CLAIMS.CLAIM_TRANSACTIONS.CLAIM_TRANSACTION_ID": "fdb84e8a-3e20-b3a8-0cf1-cea85c87cfd2"        }    },    {        $unwind: "$CLAIMS"    },    {        $unwind: "$CLAIMS.CLAIM_TRANSACTIONS"    },    {        $match: {            "CLAIMS.CLAIM_TRANSACTIONS.CLAIM_TRANSACTION_ID": "fdb84e8a-3e20-b3a8-0cf1-cea85c87cfd2"        }    },    {        $project: {            _id: 0,             FIRST: 1,            LAST: 1        }    },    {        $group: {            _id: {                FIRST: "$FIRST",                LAST: "$LAST"            }        }    },    {        $project: {            _id: 0,             FIRST: "$_id.FIRST",            LAST: "$_id.LAST"        }    }]);

question: What is the type of the allergy with the code 256277009?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX snomed: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#snomed:SNOMED-CT> SELECT DISTINCT ?type WHERE { ?allergy a syn:Allergy ; syn:code '256277009'^^snomed:; syn:type ?type; }
sql: SELECT DISTINCT type  FROM allergies WHERE code='256277009';

question: In which encounter was the imaging study with the series UID 1.2.840.99999999.1.94906246.1703949012410 conducted?
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX uuid: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#urn:uuid> SELECT  DISTINCT ?description WHERE { ?imagingstudy a syn:ImagingStudy; syn:seriesUid '1.2.840.99999999.1.94906246.1703949012410'^^uuid:; syn:encounterId ?encounterId. ?encounter a syn:Encounter; syn:id ?encounterId; syn:description ?description. }
sql: SELECT e.description FROM imaging_studies ims LEFT JOIN encounters e ON ims.encounter=e.id  WHERE ims.series_uid='1.2.840.99999999.1.94906246.1703949012410';

question: Give me the base cost of the immunization Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free.
sparql: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> PREFIX syn: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#> PREFIX xsd: <http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#> PREFIX pl: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#PlainLiteral> SELECT DISTINCT ?cost WHERE { ?immunization a syn:Immunization; syn:description 'Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free'^^pl:; syn:cost ?cost. }
sql: SELECT DISTINCT base_cost FROM immunizations WHERE description='Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free';
cypher: MATCH (i:Immunization {description: 'Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free'}) RETURN DISTINCT i.baseCost;
mql: db.patients.aggregate([    { $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.IMMUNIZATIONS.DESCRIPTION": "Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free"} },    { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS" },    { $unwind: "$ENCOUNTERS.IMMUNIZATIONS" },    { $match: {"ENCOUNTERS.IMMUNIZATIONS.DESCRIPTION": "Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free"} },    { $group: {_id: "$ENCOUNTERS.IMMUNIZATIONS.BASE_COST"}},    { $project: { _id: 0, base_cost: "$_id" } }])
